{"tid":1069814,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個前度發顛時候對你做過既痴線野","createTime":"2019-03-20T08:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T03:54:34.000Z","uid":240952,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad387341222dc74fd0219431417b0e0bc21dea1","tid":1069814,"uid":240952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"有個前度當年做左啲野搞到佢自己呀爸都唔想再理佢。<br />\n<br />\n有一晚佢崩潰左打俾我然後係咁搵啲小事黎鬧我. 我廢鬼事再彩佢所以cut 佢線。我同佢講我唔舒服唔想再講，跟著佢成晚由凌晨一點開始到好似三/四點連續打左廿幾個電話俾我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nBlock 佢電話, 佢就用 WhatsApp 打, 再 block 就用 fb messager 打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n然後我訓醒就見到佢個 msg 話佢喺我屋企樓下. 心諗我其實趕住返工唔得閒理你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68e2492fa416fe6513f8cd09b7ec027af912021","tid":1069814,"uid":185824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"朋友個前度，佢自己提分手，分手後見到我frd拍拖狂打畀佢求婚，一晚30個電話，嗰陣佢自己都有女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n係咪同一個人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f8212ed4a6c7f3b31caaa86d6775907d775bc5","tid":1069814,"uid":240952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f68e2492fa416fe6513f8cd09b7ec027af912021","tid":1069814,"uid":185824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"朋友個前度，佢自己提分手，分手後見到我frd拍拖狂打畀佢求婚，一晚30個電話，嗰陣佢自己都有女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n係咪同一個人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"無咁橋掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf5f18e2a16ed94092f26fd4eb04c0036f04ed1","tid":1069814,"uid":126615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f68e2492fa416fe6513f8cd09b7ec027af912021","tid":1069814,"uid":185824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyT